Walter MUCKLE, Plaintiff-Appellee, v. SWORD LINE, Inc., Defendant-Appellant. No. 270, Docket 24949. United States Court of Appeals Second Circuit. Argued March 25, 1958. Decided March 25, 1958. Theodore J. Breitwieser, New York City, for defendant-appellant. Bernard Rolnick, New York City (Milton H. Spiero, New York City, on the brief), for plaintiff-appellee.

Before CLARK, Chief Judge, LUMBARD, Circuit Judge, and DIMOCK, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed in open court for want of a final order.
